      { number: 14, arabic: 'وَمَا هُوَ بِٱلۡهَزۡلِ', translation: 'And it is not amusement.' },
      { number: 15, arabic: 'إِنَّهُمۡ یَكِیدُونَ كَیۡدࣰا', translation: 'Indeed, they are planning a plan,' },
      { number: 16, arabic: 'وَأَكِیدُ كَیۡدࣰا', translation: 'But I am planning a plan.' },
      { number: 17, arabic: 'فَمَهِّلِ ٱلۡكَـٰفِرِینَ أَمۡهِلۡهُمۡ رُوَیۡدَۢا', translation: 'So allow time for the disbelievers. Leave them awhile.' }
