    story: 'Surah Ash-Shams was revealed in Makkah. It swears by the sun, the moon, the day, and the soul, and tells of the people of Thamud who rejected the she-camel. It teaches that success is for those who purify themselves.',
    verseAudioBaseUrl: 'https://everyayah.com/data/Saood_ash-Shuraym_128kbps',
